      <bioghist>
         <head>Biographical/Historical Information</head>
         <p>This church was constituted in Charlotte County, Virginia
         in 1785. In 1865, the black members requested and were granted
         permission to organize a separate church.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>These minutes cover the period from June 1823 to March
         1869. Membership lists appear on pages 145-202.</p>
